r f BC-STATES-AWARDS-PA     09-08 0117
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-STATES-AWARDS-PA </SLUG>

<TEXT>
<P>
   &QL;  PA Contract Awards By Jimmy Chuang States News Service
Washington, September 8 -- Kampi Components Co. Inc. of Fairless
Hills won a $61,744 contract from the Defense Industrial Supply
Center in Philadelphia for hardware and abrasives.
</P>
<P>
   Eaton Aerospace LLC of Glenolden won a $97,916 contract from the
Defense General Supply Center in Richmond, Va., for metallic
particle detectors.
</P>
<P>
   SPD Technologies Inc. of Philadelphia won a $131,994 contract
from the U.S. Navy in Mechanicsburg, Pa., for circuit breakers.
</P>
<P>
   Trevose Industrial Products Inc. of Macungie won a $76,474
contract from the Defense Supply Center in Columbus, Ohio, for
electromagnetic relays.
</P>
