<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-08 13:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6155 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-TEN-COLLINS-COLUMN-BO     09-08 0870
</HEADER>
