<P>
   CNN-FYI _ CNN predicts it will turn a profit on a new Web site
aimed at teachers and the millions of school children who go online
for homework help. CNN executives say the site doesn't have ads,
but they have signed on three companies that are paying to have
their logos, names and links appear on the site. The Web site,
CNNfyi.com, officially launches Monday. (Kempner, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
