display Friday, talking to people in a cafeteria and recalling his
failed congressional race in 1976 when, he said, he didn't take
enough time to talk with voters. But all hasn't changed; the RNC
put out an ad on Friday that so far is the harshest of the
campaign, attacking Al Gore on campaign finance. By Alison
Mitchell.
