does on the map that plots the season for Miami and the RedHawks
better keep that in mind today as they face Eastern Michigan, a
detour ominously sandwiched between last Saturday's emotionally
draining season-opening win at Vanderbilt and next Saturday's
historic visit to Ohio State. (Dayton Daily News)
