   BOOK-ROSE (Undated) _ In ``Red Rose Crew'' Daniel J. Boyne,
director of recreational rowing at Harvard University, looks at the
wild passion and ragged strength that stoked a winning boat and
helped usher in a new era for women's sports. By Ellen Clegg.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; FINANCIAL (f) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   ONBUSINESS-COLUMN (Undated) _ CMGI, the company that became
famous as an Internet incubator, continues to evolve into an
operating company. By Steven Syre and Charles Stein.
</P>
<P>
   REEBOK-TURNAROUND (Canton, Mass.) _ Sure, Reebok International
has some swell new fall and spring sneaker lines _ and a handsome
new headquarters to boot _ but is the company's long overdue
comeback finally at hand? By Chris Reidy. 1020 words. PHOTO
</P>
