</P>
<P>
   BBA-HOLLEY-COLUMN (Boston) -- It's renewal time for the Red
Sox-Yankees rivalry. By Michael Holley.
</P>
<P>
   FBC-COMMENT (Undated) _ College football is not like the NFL,
where there is generally a reasonable amount of stability from
season to season. By Mark Blaudschun. 1380 words.
</P>
<P>
   TV-SPORTS-COLUMN (Undated) -- ``Monday Night Football'' talk is
music to Don Ohlmeyer's ears. By Howard Manly.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
