   NATIONAL NEWS (``a'' category)
</P>
<P>
   US-CHINA (New York) _ President Clinton and Chinese President
Jiang Zemin meet, with trade deals and human rights concerns
topping their discussions. By PATTY REINERT.
</P>
<P>
   NASA-SHUTTLE (Cape Canaveral, Fla.) _ The shuttle Atlantis and
its crew of seven sped toward a weekend rendezvous with the
international space station, following a flawless lift off early
Friday. By MARK CARREAU.
</P>
