getting onto BidBay's site by sending continual useless data, like
a crank caller with speed dial. By Robert Monroe. (Will also move
on the ``f'' financial and ``n'' California news wires.)
</P>
<P>
   TOY-MOVIESET (Hollywood, Calif.) _ Straight from Hollywood: the
