<P>
   INSIDE TODAY
</P>
<P>
   About the series
</P>
<P>
   _ Today: At age 90, Chuck Gross knows he's ``living on borrowed
time,'' but he's determined to meet death on his own terms.
</P>
<P>
   _ Monday: Are we paying too much for hopeless cases? The
medical, legal and ethical issues.
</P>
<P>
   _ Tuesday: The role of doctors in the battle between life and
death.
</P>
<P>
   _ Wednesday: Easing the financial strain on families.
</P>
<P>
   _ Thursday: Losing Carol: One man's love story.
</P>
