 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 
 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    COMMUNIST CADDIES? Fidel Castro tees off on capitalism's
favorite pastime, but will golf attract tourist dollars to Cuba?
 &HT;    Filed as BC-CUBA-GOLF-RESORT-LATINTRADE-NYTSF in ``f''
financial, ``t'' travel and ``s'' sports.
