<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-09-08 20:15 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6949 &Cx1f; tab-z
r s BC-CUBA-GOLF-RESORT-LATI     09-08 1379
