defeat, Venus Williams summoned her fading strength to win four
straight games Friday, take out Martina Hingis in an exquisite
match and reach the U.S. Open final against Lindsay Davenport. By
Selena Roberts. (Scheduled to move by 10 p.m. ET in ``s'' news
file.)
</P>
<P>
   The story runs under a 2-column photo; photos
NYT12,13,14,15,32,33.
</P>
<P>
   EU-AUSTRIA (Paris) _ A panel of experts assessing human rights
and political life in Austria clears the way for the European Union
to lift diplomatic sanctions hurriedly imposed last January after
the Austrians allowed a far right party into national government.
By Suzanne Daley. (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET in ``i'' news
file.) 1,400 words.
</P>
<P>
   INSIDE STORIES PROMOTED ON PAGE 1:
</P>
<P>
